Installing Flask OpenERP Sale Payment
=====================================

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Flask (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Flask)
 * Flask-Babel (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Flask-Babel)
 * Flask-WTF (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Flask-WTF)
 * ERPPeek (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ERPpeek)
 * Sermepa (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/sermepa)
 * Paypal (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/paypal)

Configuration
-------------

config.ini

* APP NAME

config.cfg

* Debug
* Template
* Language
* Payments

